Formal targets

1. Spec update

File

* ConversionFront_v3.tla

Required changes

* modify BuildCompress
* ensure the reachable front no longer lies on a single affine line in (r,s) projection
* preserve existing safety invariants unless explicitly superseded

New derived property

Add a property or checked theorem equivalent to:

There exist reachable front points P_1, P_2, P_3 such that they are not collinear in projected (r,s) space.

Possible formal expression shape:

NonDegenerateFront ==
  \E p1, p2, p3 \in ReachableFront :
    ~CollinearRS(p1, p2, p3)

If you already have front extraction helpers, bind to them. If not, add minimal helpers without broadening spec complexity.

