UI changes

Objective

Make the operator surface accurately reflect geometry class without pretending to prove anything.

Target surfaces

* IntelBlocks
* SignalsPage
* any advanced-mode badge or geometry descriptor

Required display behavior

In 2D mode

Show something like:

